  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The contingent beneficiary, which will receive the death benefit if the primary beneficiary predeceases the insured. The trust is established to manage the funds for the benefit of the family."</data>
