  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"FINANCIAL_CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The amount a policyholder receives if they voluntarily terminate the policy before maturity, calculated as the accumulated cash value minus any loans, fees, or surrender charges."&lt;SEP&gt;"The amount received under the cash surrender option."&lt;SEP&gt;"The cash surrender value is reduced by outstanding loans and accrued interest."&lt;SEP&gt;"The cash surrender value is the amount available for loan or withdrawal."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-4f8527575d3cf5f681b0be617575250d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50bd298a3b0f04dca6e62ad3a0259fac</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DOB: JULY 8, 1978&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DATE"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The date of birth of the insured, used to determine age, premium rates, and maturity date."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-50bd298a3b0f04dca6e62ad3a0259fac</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;EXTENDED TERM INSURANCE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"OPTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A non-forfeiture option that maintains the full face amount for a limited time using the cash value."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-4f8527575d3cf5f681b0be617575250d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;INVESTMENT EXPERIENCE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"FINANCIAL_CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The performance of the insurer’s investment portfolio, which affects the profitability and potential for dividends."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-50bd298a3b0f04dca6e62ad3a0259fac</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LOAN INTEREST RATE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"FINANCIAL_CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The loan interest rate is 5% per annum, compounded annually."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-4f8527575d3cf5f681b0be617575250d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ISSUE AGE: 45&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"AGE"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The age of the insured at the time the policy was issued, which affects premium calculations and underwriting."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-50bd298a3b0f04dca6e62ad3a0259fac</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;INTEREST&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"FINANCIAL CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Interest is not applied to the premiums paid, indicating a flat payment structure."&lt;SEP&gt;"Interest on policy loans during reinstatement."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f4df5d777eaf88d69afa87f3f4bd50c0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f8527575d3cf5f681b0be617575250d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;EXPENSE EXPERIENCE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"FINANCIAL_CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The actual operating expenses of the insurer compared to projected expenses, which impacts profitability and dividend potential."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-50bd298a3b0f04dca6e62ad3a0259fac</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;5% PER ANNUM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"FINANCIAL_RATE"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The annual interest rate on the loan is 5%, compounded yearly."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-4f8527575d3cf5f681b0be617575250d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RISK CLASS: STANDARD NON-TOBACCO&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CLASSIFICATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A risk classification indicating that the insured is considered a standard risk and does not use tobacco, which affects premium rates."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-50bd298a3b0f04dca6e62ad3a0259fac</data>
</node>
